Package org.openpnp.spi

Interface FiducialLocator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    PropertySheetHolder
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ReferenceFiducialLocator
    public interface FiducialLocator
extends PropertySheetHolder
    Provides a method to detect and orient boards using a fiducial system. This interface is primarily implemented by the ReferenceFidicualLocator but is provided so that future expansion can occur without requiring configuration changes.
